ave been made based on\n$\\mathrm{SFR_{UV+IR}}$ measurements alone, highlighting the power of detailed\nSFH modeling in the interpretation of gas reservoirs. Larger samples are needed\nto understand the frequency of low-level rejuvenation among quiescent galaxies\nat intermediate redshifts, and to what extent this drives the diversity of\nmolecular gas reservoirs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 22:12:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2023 20:48:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-06"}
